( openstack-nova-novncproxy)

Compute VNC proxy for traditional	6081
VNC clients (openstack-nova-xvpvncproxy)

Proxy port for HTML5 console used 	6082
by Compute service

Data processing service 		8386
(sahara) endpoint

Identity service (keystone) 		35357
administrative endpoint

Identity service public endpoint	5000

Image service (glance) API		9292

